task.summary: Move old release notes to unsupported list. Also a bit of whitespace change since this is the first time I've opened the docs with the new Intellij Ultimate version.
Put the docbook xsd file into the project to allow Intellij to validate against it. Fix some namespace attribute issues. No functional change.
Fix escaping of & in the release notes
Our repo is on SSL only
Tidy up the docbook classes and put them out of the way into buildSrc to make them tidy.
Restructure the onCourse docs folders to make everything easier to change and package.
Don't build the PDF for now.
Set up to publish snapshots and releases to repo.
Make the top level publishing task work (the top of the gradle tree has itself nothing to publish)
Rename the apidocs project to dsl which is rather more correct
